data.description:
Main Floor Flex room, could easily serve as a 5th Bedroom. Front railing and stair will be repaired before closing. Projector in basement included inWelcome home to this Gorgeous Mod 2 story in Prestigious South Oaks Pond of Blaine. This home offers many recent updates Including: Newer Roof, siding, furnace, Stainless appliances, water heater, carpet, and Central Air. Main floor mud/laundry. The heated/insulated 3 car garage comes
fully equipped with ceiling fan, electrical, in addition to a bonus 2nd level for a workshop or
additional storage! Upper level offers 3 bedrooms including your master suite with jetted tub stand alone shower,  and a walk-in closet! Lower level is completely finished with high ceilings, and a newly added 3/4 Bath! All this on a corner lot, with a full privacy fence, and gorgeous deck to enjoy those summer BBQ's. Act
Fast- This one will not last
